modules.description: This library provides functions to generate random values of primitive types (integers, floats, booleans, etc.) and combinators to construct structured test data like pairs, lists, and result types. It supports property-based testing by enabling dynamic generator binding, custom test output printers, and control mechanisms to filter invalid cases or inject failures. Assertion utilities allow precise validation of conditions, equality checks, and error handling with customizable messages, particularly useful for testing complex logic or edge cases in arbitrary data.
